# c/MessageHeap

ApproxDuration: ""
DependsOn: "c/MessageSystem"

# Description
class MessageHeap { (static) list<Message*> };

There is a "global" way to add messages to the MessageHeap.
The Game can poll these Messages, and broadcast them to the necessary Listeners.

[c/Game: class Game; -- The superior modular unit]

